    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/e7d5169a76d11f7ffbbdd9e939856a10.avif?t=1734612401\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>欢迎来到 'Arcus Chroma' 的起源，这是由独立游戏开发者 GxGrainson 用心创造的一项爱的结晶（制作者向您问好！）。这是一场充满激情的冒险，这款创新的格斗游戏拥有独特的'Hyper-Flow'战斗风格，去除了跳跃按钮，并重新定位以增强游戏的所有其他机制。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>当前抢先体验功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 本地对战模式（对玩家和CPU）<br></li><li> 训练模式<br></li><li> 10个可玩角色<br></li><li> 4个场景<br></li><li> 设置与按键配置<br></li><li> 更多功能计划中！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/1835d3dc7881ca6f6b90bc920fa61f3e.avif?t=1734612401\" width=600 height=561 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不跳跃？在一个格斗游戏中？</strong></h2>告别跳跃，拥抱全新的刺激，专注于掌握连击创作和地面战斗的艺术。将快速、流畅的移动选项与令人满意的闪避机制相结合，绕过对手并计划反击。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/8cee533d31d2bb8be15cf2b01c36107f.poster.avif?t=1734612401\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/8cee533d31d2bb8be15cf2b01c36107f.webm?t=1734612401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/8cee533d31d2bb8be15cf2b01c36107f.mp4?t=1734612401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>连击创意</strong></h2>凭借多样化的角色阵容和创新的创意连击系统，Arcus Chroma 提供了一个令人振奋且新鲜的游戏体验，您可以打造自己的个性化游戏风格，前所未有地统治战场！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/953e48f4475e7a32a838f8895b834728.poster.avif?t=1734612401\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/953e48f4475e7a32a838f8895b834728.webm?t=1734612401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/953e48f4475e7a32a838f8895b834728.mp4?t=1734612401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/f6ebf4ed9d42895e22921c2235003933.avif?t=1734612401\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Steam 远程游玩 &amp; Parsec</strong></h2>在当前版本中，'Arcus Chroma：Classic' 不支持在线多人游戏——这是独立开发者面临的独特挑战的结果。然而，我们强烈鼓励玩家利用 Steam 的'远程游玩'功能或第三方应用程序如 'Parsec' 与朋友和对手一起享受在线对战。<br><br>展望更宏伟的未来，GxGrainson 希望通过《Arcus Chroma：空间转移》扩展 Arcus Chroma 宇宙，该续集将改进游戏玩法，具备回溯网络代码和跨平台游玩功能。您的支持推动着 GxGrainson 的使命，为 'Arcus Chroma' 的发展铺平道路，并为未来的努力奠定基础。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/f07fdd90fd7c59d30278709b14f65bf5.poster.avif?t=1734612401\" width=598 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/f07fdd90fd7c59d30278709b14f65bf5.webm?t=1734612401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/f07fdd90fd7c59d30278709b14f65bf5.mp4?t=1734612401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447350/extras/bafd9255e8d4b129c4520b14f1716a2e.avif?t=1734612401\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>对于 'Arcus Chroma：Classic'，GxGrainson 相信社区合作和透明度的力量。<br><br>加入我们友好的社区，您的想法将塑造游戏的未来。深入讨论角色概念、攻击策略、舞台美学和丰富的色彩搭配。在这里，每个声音都被听到和重视，为一个支持性和协作性的环境做出贡献。<br><br>成为我们 Discord 的活跃社区的一部分，让我们共同创造一个反映每位玩家集体创造力和热情的游戏体验。您的声音很重要；让我们一起打造我们所憧憬的 'Arcus Chroma' 冒险！【点击下方图像！】<br>",
